reviews.review_text:
Rainforest Party Jerry's voice is shot and this may not be the show for the Deadhead Purist (whatever that is) but if you want to hear how the boys throw a party than this is the show for you! The sound quality is good for a crowd recording. Long live the animals.
-Squirrel
